      <p>Hello Admin,</p>
      <p>A new investment has just been submitted. Below are the details:</p>

      <div class="info-box">
        <p><span class="highlight">Name:</span> <%= name %></p>
        <p><span class="highlight">Profession:</span> <%= profession %></p>
        <p><span class="highlight">Email:</span> <%= email %></p>
        <p><span class="highlight">WhatsApp:</span> <%= whatsapp %></p>
        <p><span class="highlight">Amount Invested:</span> $<%= amount %></p>
      </div>

      <p>Please review and verify this investment in the system at your earliest convenience.</p>

